i.dk/?q=content/jason-derulo-marry-me|publisher= [[IFPI Denmark]]|language=Danish}}</ref>|type=single|certmonth=9|salesamount=900,000}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|format=3col}}\n\n==Credits and personnel==\n* [[Vocals]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Jason Derulo]]\n* [[Lyrics]]&nbsp;\u2013 Jason Desrouleaux, Jonas Jeberg, \u201cHookman\u201d Marlin Bonds, Andy Marvel\n* [[Record producer|Producer]]&nbsp;\u2013 Jonas Jeberg\n* [[Record label|Label]]&nbsp;\u2013 Warner Bros. Records Inc.\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"column\"| Region !! Date !! Format !! Label\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Canada<ref>https://itunes.apple.com/ca/album/marry-me-single/id692580887</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| August 26, 2013\n| rowspan=\"2\"| {{flat list|\n*[[Music download|Digital download]]}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Warner Music Group]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States<ref name=\"apple.com\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United States\n| rowspan=\"1\"| September 10, 2013\n| rowspan=\"1\"| {{flatlist|\n* [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n}}\n| rowspan=\"1\"| {{flatlist|\n* Warner Music Group\n* [[Beluga Heights]]\n}}\n|-\n| France\n| September 23, 2013\n| Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.fr/Marry-Me/dp/B00F2HZ09C/|title=Marry Me|publisher=|via=Amazon}}</ref>\n| Warner Music Group\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Jason Derulo}}\n\n[[Category:2013 songs]]\n[[Category:2013 singles]]\n[[Category:2010s ballads]]\n[[Category:Contemporary R&B ballads]]\n[[Category:Jason Derulo songs]]\n[[Category:Pop ballads]]\n[[Category:Songs about marriage]]\n[[Category:Music videos directed by Hannah Lux Davis]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Marry Me\n| cover      = Marry Me - Single Cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Jason Derulo]]\n| album      = [[Tattoos (album)|Tattoos]] {{noitalics|and}} [[Talk Dirty (album)|Talk Dirty]]\n| released   = September 1, 2013<ref name=\"apple.com\">https://itunes.apple.