that person forever so 105 is the number that I thought of\".<ref name=\"iheart.com\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thisisrnb.com/2013/08/new-music-jason-derulo-marry-me/|title=New Music: Jason Derulo \u2013 Marry Me  - ThisisRnB.com - Hot New R&B Music, Videos, News|website=www.thisisrnb.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5672598/jordin-sparks-engaged-to-jason-derulo-singer-plays-coy-about-a-huge-ring|title=Jordin Sparks Engaged to Jason Derulo? Singer Plays Coy About a Huge Ring|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2013/08/26/new-music-jason-derulo-marry-me/|title=New Music: Jason Derulo \u2013 'Marry Me'|website=Rap-Up}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video to \"Marry Me\" was released on Derulo's YouTube account on September 23, 2013. The video also features [[Jordin Sparks]] who appears on the video since Derulo dedicated to her.<ref>{{YouTube|zRCsZ5a3aCM}}</ref> The music video also premiered on BET's ''[[106 & Park]]'' the same day. In the video, Derulo can be seen buying a ring, waking up with Sparks, Derulo playing the pianos while Sparks lays on top. Then, other scenes include the two of them relaxing in a bath tub, watching a movie, eating and fighting with flour. The older version of Derulo and Sparks at the end were played by Derulo's grandparents.\n\n==Critical reception==\nKaren Lanza of ''Popcruch'' said Derulo \"has simultaneously granted the world its next top wedding tune and given girlfriend Jordin Sparks good reason to go shopping for a fancy white gown\" and called it an \"upbeat love song\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://popcrush.com/jason-derulo-marry-me-song-review/|title=Jason Derulo, 'Marry Me' - Song Review|website=PopCrush}}</ref> Arjanwrites.com praised Jason vocals and writing skill in the song stating \"Marry Me\" neatly shows off Derulo's vocal chops and poignant songwriting savvy. It's a heartfelt, hook laden and soaring melodic ballad with a proper stomp that drives home the key message of the song.\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arjanwrites.com/arjanwrites/2013/08/jason-derulo-marry-me-review.html|title=Review: Jason Derulo Premieres New Single 'Marry Me'|website=www.arjanwrites.com}}</ref>\n\n==Release and artwork==\nThe artwork for the single features the diamond ring seen in Derulo's CGI neck tattoo on the album cover of ''[[Tattoos (album)|Tattoos]]''. The song made its world premiere of the new song on ''[[On Air with Ryan Seacrest]]'' on Monday August 26, 2013 and was made available for digital download through digital retailers on the day.<ref name=\"iheart.com\"/>\n\n==Usage in media==\nThe song was featured in the 2014 re-release of the game ''[[Grand Theft Auto V]]'' on the fictional radio station \"[[Grand Theft Auto V soundtrack#Radio Los Santos|Radio Los Santos]]\", despite the station not playing R&B, it was also featured in [[Comedy Central]] animated series ''[[South Park]]'' episode \"[[Basic Cable (South Park)|Basic Cable]]\".\n\n==Track listing==\n* '''Digital download'''<ref name=\"apple.com\"/>\n# \"Marry Me\" \u2013 3:45\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Chart (2013\u201314)\n! Peak<br/>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|8|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|27|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia Tip|5|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canada|37|artist=Jason Derulo}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|France|50|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Germany2|57|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me|songid=1186489|accessdate=2019-03-15}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|New Zealand|14|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Switzerland|40|artist=Jason Derulo|song=Marry Me}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|UK|52|artist=Jason Derulo|date=2013-10-16}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardhot100|26|artist=Jason Derulo}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardadultpopsongs|27|artist=Jason Derulo}}\n|-\n{{si