e River]]\n** [[Le Petit Chenail (Yamaska River tributary)|Le Petit Chenail]]\n*** [[Saint-Louis River (Yamaska)|Saint-Louis River]]\n** [[Salvail River]]\n** [[South-West River (Yamaska River tributary)|South-West River]]\n** [[\u00c9cossais River]]\n** [[Yamaska Sud-Est River]]\n** [[Yamaska Nord River]]\n** [[Noire River (Yamaska River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Renne River]]\n**** [[Duncan River]]\n*** [[Jaune River (Noire River tributary)|Jaune River]]\n*** [[Rouge River (Noire River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n** [[Chibouet River]]\n** [[David River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''West bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n[[Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River]]\n* [[Vaches River]]\n* [[Little Black River (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River tributary)|Little Black River]]\n* [[Saint-Germain River]]\n* [[Ulverton River]]\n** [[Fraser River (Le Val-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Fraser River]]\n* [[Saumon River (Le Val-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Saumon River]]\n* [[Magog River]]\n** [[Lake Memphremagog]]\n*** [[Johns River (Vermont)|Johns River]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Cerises River]] (Qu\u00e9bec, Canada)\n*** [[Black River (Lake Memphremagog)|Black River]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Barton River, Vermont|Barton River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Willoughby River]] (Vermont, United States)\n***** [[Brownington Branch (Willoughby River tributary)|Brownington Branch]] (Vermont, United States)\n*** [[Clyde River (Vermont)|Clyde River]] (Vermont, United States)\n**** [[Pherrins River, Vermont]] (Vermont, United States)\n}}\n'''South bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Massawippi River]]\n** [[Coaticook River]]\n** [[Saumons River (Massawippi River tributary)|Saumons River]]\n*** [[Moe River]]\n** [[Lake Massawippi]]\n*** [[Tomifobia River]]\n**** [[Niger River]]\n* [[Eaton River]]\n** [[Clifton River]]\n** [[Eaton River North]]\n*** [[Newport River (Eaton River North)|Newport River]]\n* [[Saumon River (Le Haut-Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Saumon River]]\n** [[Chesham River]]\n** [[Ditton River]]\n*** [[Ditton River West]]\n*** [[Ditton River East]]\n* [[Rat River (Weedon)|Rat River]]\n* [[Bernier River (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River tributary)|Bernier River]]\n}}\n'''North bank of Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Moose River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Moose River]]\n* [[Coulombe River]]\n** [[Coulombe River North]]\n* [[Canard River]]\n* [[Weedon River]]\n* [[Bogue River]]\n}}\n'''[[Great Lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois]]'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Felton River]]\n** [[Sauvage River (Felton River tributary)|Sauvage River]]\n** [[Noire River (Felton River tributary)|Noire River]]\n** [[Blanche River (Felton River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Legendre River (Felton River tributary)|Legendre River]]\n* [[Little River (lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Little River]]\n* [[Blueberries River (lake Saint-Fran\u00e7ois)|Blueberries River]]\n** [[Blueberries River South]]\n* [[Little Muskrat River]]\n* [[Muskrat River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Muskrat River]]\n* [[Or River]]\n* [[Ashberham River]]\n}}\n'''Lake Noir (Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River)'''\n* [[Bisby River]]\n* [[Coleraine River]]\n\n'''East bank of [[Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River]]'''\n\n* [[Watopeka River]]\n** [[Stoke River]]\n\n'''Tributaries upstream of [[Saint-Fran\u00e7ois River]]'''\n\n* [[L\u00e9vesque River]]\n* [[Colbert River]]\n* [[Landroche River]]\n* [[Fr\u00e8res River]]\n\n=== Watershed of Nicolet River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Nicolet River]]\n**[[Nicolet River Southwest]]\n*** [[Saint-Z\u00e9phirin River]]\n*** [[S\u00e9v\u00e8re-Ren\u00e9 River]]\n*** [[Landry River (Estrie)|Rivi\u00e8re Landry]]\n**** [[Danville River]]\n*** [[Carmel River]]\n*** [[Lafont River]]\n*** [[Pat River]]\n*** [[Nicolet Centre River]]\n**** [[Nicolet North-East River]]\n*** [[Dion River (Les Sources)|Dion River]]\n*** [[Saint-Camille River]]\n***