omaine River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Etchemin River ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n'''Tributaries of west bank''':\n* [[Penin River]]\n* [[Le Bras (Etchemin River tributary)|Le Bras]]\n* [[Desbarats River]]\n* [[Pyke River (Etchemin River tributary)|Pyke River]]\n* [[Henderson River]]\n* [[Viveine River]]\n\n'''Tributaries of south bank''':\n* [[Lanigan River]]\n* [[Discharge of lake Etchemin]]\n* [[Etchemin Little River]]\n* [[Bourget River]]\n\n'''Tributaries of east bank''':\n* [[Blanche River (Etchemin River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n* [[B\u0153uf River]]\n* [[Fleurs River (Etchemin River tributary)|Fleurs River]]\n* [[Eau Chaude Stream]]\n** [[Rover Stream]]\n* [[Hemison Stream]]\n* [[Ab\u00e9naquis River (Etchemin River tributary)|Ab\u00e9naquis River]]\n** [[Billots River]]\n*** [[Moulin River (Billots River tributary)|Moulin River]]\n}}\n\n==Gaspesie Peninsula==\n\n=== Watershed of southeast of St. Lawrence River (at east of Etchemin River) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Scie River]]\n** [[Couture River]]\n* [[Boyer River]]\n** [[Boyer River North]]\n** [[Boyer River South]]\n* [[M\u00e8res River]]\n** [[Blanche River (Saint-Vallier)|Blanche River]]\n* [[Lacaille River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of South River, Montmagny (French: Rivi\u00e8re du Sud) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[River South (Montmagny)|River South]]\n** [[Bras Saint-Michel]]\n*** [[Moulin River (Bras Saint-Michel)|Moulin River]]\n** [[Fourche River]]\n*** [[Mornes River]]\n*** [[Orignaux River (Fourche River tributary)|Orignaux River]]\n** [[Pine River (South River, Montmagny)|Pine River]]\n*** [[Gabriel River]]\n**** [[River North (Gabriel River tributary)|River North]]\n** [[Loutre River (river South)|Loutre River]]\n** [[Alick River]]\n*** [[Moulin River (Alick River tributary)|Moulin River]]\n** [[Fraser River (river South)|Fraser River]]\n** [[Little River Sainte-Marguerite]]\n** [[Minguy River]]\n** [[Morigeau River]]\n*** [[Poitras River]]\n** [[Bras Saint-Nicolas]]\n*** [[Perdrix River (Bras Saint-Nicolas)|Perdrix River]]\n**** [[Inconnue River (Perdrix River tributary)|Inconnue River]]\n*** [[Cloutier River]]\n*** [[Bras d'Apic]]\n*** [[Bras de Riche]]\n**** [[Bras North-East (Bras de Riche)|Bras North-East]]\n*** [[M\u00e9chant Pouce River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of southeast bank of St. Lawrence River (at east of South River, Montmagny) ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Vincelotte River]]\n* [[Tortue River (L'Islet)|Tortue River]]\n** [[Tortue River South-West]]\n*** [[Petit Moulin River (Tortue River South-West)|Petit Moulin River]]\n* [[Trois Saumons River]]\n** [[Trois Saumons River East]]\n* [[Port Joli River]]\n* [[Ferr\u00e9e River (L'Islet)|Ferr\u00e9e River]]\n** [[Le Bras (Ferr\u00e9e River tributary)|Le Bras]]\n** [[Joncas River (Ferr\u00e9e River tributary)|Joncas River]]\n**[[Rouget River]]\n* [[Saint-Jean River (La Pocati\u00e8re)|Saint-Jean River]]\n* [[Ouelle River]]\n** [[Damn\u00e9e River]]\n** [[La Grande Rivi\u00e8re (Ouelle River tributary)|La Grande Rivi\u00e8re]]\n*** [[Chaude River (La Grande Rivi\u00e8re)|Chaude River]]\n*** [[Sainte-Anne River (La Grande Rivi\u00e8re)|Sainte-Anne River]]\n*** [[Rat Musqu\u00e9 River]]\n** [[Bras de la rivi\u00e8re Ouelle]]\n* [[Kamouraska River]] (ex-rivi\u00e8re aux Perles)\n** [[Dufour River]]\n** [[Saint-Denis River (Kamouraska River tributary)|Saint-Denis River]]\n*** [[Bouteillerie River]]\n*** [[Bras de la Rivi\u00e8re Saint-Denis]]\n** [[Goudron River]]\n* [[Fouquette River]]\n* [[Caps River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Rivi\u00e8re du Loup and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Rivi\u00e8re du Loup (Bas-Saint-Laurent)|Rivi\u00e8re du Loup]]\n** [[Pivard River]]\n** [[Le Grand Bras (rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Le Grand Bras]]\n** [[Manie River]]\n** [[Loutres River (rivi\u00e8re du Loup)|Loutres River]]\n** [[Fourchue River]]\n*** [[Carrier River]]\n*** [[Rocheuse River (lake Morin)|Rocheuse River]]\n**** [[Noire River (Rocheuse Ri