au River]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re de la Montagne Blanche]]\n*[[Rapides River]]\n*[[Moisie River]]\n**[[Kachiwiss River]]\n**[[Ouapetec River]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re aux P\u00e9kans]]\n***[[Carhel River]]\n***[[Crasse River]]\n**[[Taoti River]]\n**[[Petite rivi\u00e8re Taoti]]\n**[[Joseph River]]\n**[[Rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 l'Eau Dor\u00e9e]]\n**[[Nipissis River]]\n***[[Mistamoue River]] (via [[lake Siamois]])\n****[[Matinipi River]]\n***[[Wacouno River]]\n***[[Nipisso River]]\n***[[McDonald River]]\n***[[Petite rivi\u00e8re \u00e0 la Truite (Moisie River tributary)]]\n*[[Matamec River]]\n*[[Loups Marins River]]\n*[[Pigou River]]\n**[[Pigou-Est River]]\n*[[Bouleau River]]\n*[[Rivi\u00e8re du Sault Plat]]\n*[[Tortue River]]\n*[[Manitou River (Quebec)|Manitou River]]\n*[[Vibert River]]\n*[[Sheldrake River (Minganie)|Sheldrake River]]\n*[[Jim-Hearst River]]\n*[[Tonnerre River (Minganie)]]\n*[[Br\u00fbl\u00e9e River]]{{dn|date=March 2020}}\n*[[B\u00e9line River]] \n*[[Magpie River (Quebec)|Magpie River]]\n*[[Magpie River East]]\n*[[Saint-C\u0153ur River]]\n*[[Saint-Jean River (Minganie)|Saint-Jean River]]\n**[[M\u00e9o River]]\n*[[Mingan River]]\n*[[Kamenakapeu River]]\n}}\n\n===Tributaries downstream of Romaine River===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*[[Romaine River]] (Newfoundland-Qu\u00e9bec)\n**[[Cinq River]] (rivi\u00e8re des Cinq)\n**[[Brochets River]] (rivi\u00e8re aux Brochets)\n**[[Fleurs River]] (rivi\u00e8re aux Fleurs)\n**[[P\u00eacheurs River]] (rivi\u00e8re aux P\u00eacheurs)\n**[[Discharge of Lake Pommerel]] (Newfoundland)\n**[[S\u00e9n\u00e9chal River]] (Newfoundland)\n**[[Discharge of Lake Norman]] (Newfoundland-Quebec))\n**[[Sauterelles River]]\n**[[Touladis River]]\n**[[Little Romaine River]]\n**[[Glapion River]]\n**[[Garneau River (Romaine River)]]\n***[[Garneau River West]]\n**[[Abb\u00e9 Huard River]]\n**[[Bernard River]]\n**[[Romaine River Southwest]]\n**[[Maleck River]]\n**[[Puyjalon River]]\n***[[Bat-le-Diable River]]\n***[[Allard River (Puylalon River tri