rces)|Dion River]]\n*** [[Saint-Camille River]]\n**** [[Madeleine River (Les Sources)|Madeleine River]]\n**[[Bulstrode River]]\n** [[Nicolet South-West River]]\n** [[Bulstrode River]]\n*** [[Blanche River (Bulstrode River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Bulstrode River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[L'Abb\u00e9 River]]\n**[[Gosselin River (Nicolet River tributary)|Gosselin River]]\n*** [[Lachance River]]\n** [[Des Rosiers River]]\n** [[Des Pins River (Nicolet River tributary)|Des Pins River]]\n** [[Brooks River]]\n** [[Dumont River]]\n** [[Blanche River (Nicolet River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Des Vases River]]\n* [[Godefroy River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of B\u00e9cancour River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[B\u00e9cancour River]]\n** [[Judith River]]\n** [[Portage River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|Portage River]]\n** [[Gagnon River]]\n** [[Blanche River (B\u00e9cancour)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Goulet River]]\n** [[Bourbon River]]\n*** [[Blanche River (Bourbon River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Noire River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Barbue River]]\n*** [[Perdrix River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|Perdrix River]]\n** [[Palmer River]]\n*** [[Osgood River]]\n**** [[Sunday River]]\n**** [[Gagn\u00e9 River]]\n*** [[Palmer Est River]]\n*** [[Perry River]]\n*** [[Whetstone River]]\n** [[McKenzie River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|McKenzie River]]\n** [[Dubois River]] (named in the pas \"Chainey River\")\n** [[Bagot River]]\n** [[Larochelle River]]\n** [[Pine River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|Pine River]]\n*** [[Blanche River (Pine River tributary)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Blanche River (Thetford Mines)|Blanche River]]\n** [[Moulin River (B\u00e9cancour River tributary)|Moulin River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Gentilly River and Eastern tributaries ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Gentilly River]]\n** [[Gentilly South-West River]]\n*** [[Grand-Saint-Louis River]]\n** [[Sauvage River (Gentilly River tributary)|Sauvage River]]\n** [[Beaudet River (Gentilly River tributary)|Beaudet River]]\n* [[De la Ferme River]]\n* [[Moulin River (Gentilly)|Moulin River]]\n* [[Glaises River]]\n* [[Orignaux River (Gentilly)|Orignaux River]]\n* [[Ch\u00eane Little River]]\n** [[Ormes River (Fortierville)|Ormes River]]\n** [[Creuse River (Fortierville)|Creuse River]]\n* [[Ch\u00eane River (Leclercville)|Ch\u00eane River]]\n** [[Chevreuils River]]\n** [[Saint-Georges River (Ch\u00eane River tributary)|Saint-Georges River]]\n** [[Huron River (Ch\u00eane River tributary)|Huron River]]\n*** [[Ormes River (Huron River tributary)|Ormes River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Huron River tributary)|Noire River]]\n** [[Henri River (Lotbini\u00e8re)|Henri River]]\n*** [[C\u00e8dres River]]\n*** [[Fr\u00eanes River]]\n** [[Bois Clair River]]\n* [[Aulneuse River]]\n}}\n\n=== Watershed of Chaudi\u00e8re River ===\n'''Tributaries of west bank of Richelieu River'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Chaudi\u00e8re River]]\n** [[Beaurivage River]]\n*** [[Rouge River (Beaurivage River tributary)|Rouge River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Beaurivage River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Pine River (Beaurivage River tributary)|Pine River]]\n*** [[Filkars River]]\n**** [[Armagh River]]\n**** [[Saint-Andr\u00e9 River]]\n**** [[Fourchette River]]\n*** [[Bras d'Henri River]]\n*** [[Cugnet River]]\n** [[\u00celes Br\u00fbl\u00e9es River]]\n** [[Vall\u00e9e River]]\n** [[Savoie River]]\n** [[Nadeau River (Nouvelle-Beauce)|Nadeau River]]\n** [[Lessard River (Chaudi\u00e8re River tributary)|Lessard River]]\n** [[Cliche River]]\n** [[Fermes River]]\n** [[Bras Saint-Victor]]\n*** [[Cinq River]]\n*** [[Pr\u00e9vost-Gilbert River]]\n**** [[Noire River (Pr\u00e9vost-Gilbert River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Hamel River]]\n** [[Moulin River (Beauceville)|Moulin River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Moulin River tributary)|Noire River]]\n*** [[Meules Brook (Moulin River tributary)|Meules Brook]]\n** [[Pozer River]]\n** [[Shenley River]]\n** [[Grande Coud\u00e9e River]]\n** [[Petit Portage River]]\n** [[Ludgine River]]\n** [[Drolet River]]\n** [[Madisson River]]\n** [[Glen River (Chaudi\u00e8re River tributary)|Glen River]]\n** [[Lake M\u00e9gantic]]\n*** [[Victoria River (lake M\u00e9gantic)|Victoria River]]\n*** [[Bergeron River]]\n*** [[Araign\u00e9es River]]\n**** [[Indiens River (lake aux Araign\u00e9es)|Indiens River]]\n**** [[Arnold River (lake aux Araign\u00e9es)|Arnold River]]\n***** [[Clinton River]]\n}}\n'''Tributaries of east bank of [[Chaudi\u00e8re River]]'''\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Nebnellis River]]\n** [[Kokombis River]]\n* [[Samson River (Chaudi\u00e8re River tributary)|Samson River]]\n** [[Barrage River]]\n*** [[Renards River]]\n* [[Moulin River (Saint-G\u00e9d\u00e9on)|Moulin River]]\n* [[Truite River (Chaudi\u00e8re River tributary)|Truite River]]\n* [[Loup River (Chaudi\u00e8re River tributary)|Loup River]]\n** [[Taschereau River]]\n** [[Caouette Stream]]\n** [[Monument River]]\n*** [[Monument Little River]]\n** [[Portage River (Beauce-Sartigan)|Portage River]]\n*** [[Portage River North (Beauce-Sartigan)|Portage River North]]\n** [[Wilson River (Beauce-Sartigan)|Wilson River]]\n** [[Metgermette River]]\n*** [[Metgermette River South]]\n*** [[Metgermette River Centrale]]\n*** [[Metgermette River North]]\n** [[Vachon River (Beauce-Sartigan)|Vachon River]]\n* [[Famine River]]\n** [[Ab\u00e9naquis River]]\n*** [[Ab\u00e9naquis River South-West]]\n*** [[Ab\u00e9naquis River South-East]]\n** [[Veilleux River]]\n** [[Raquette River (Famine River tributary)|Raquette River]]\n** [[Flamand River (Les Etchemins)|Flamand River]]\n** [[Cumberland River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Cumberland River]]\n* [[Gilbert River (Beauce-Sartigan)|Gilbert River]]\n* [[Plante River]]\n** [[Fraser River (Plante River tributary)|Fraser River]]\n*** [[Noire River (Fraser River tributary)|Noire River]]\n* [[Calway River]]\n* [[Pouliot River]]\n* [[Morency River]]\n* [[Belair River]]\