es River]] (or \"Fivemile Brook\" in Maine)\n*** [[Deux Milles River (Quebec-Maine)|Deux Milles River]] (or \"Twomile Brook\" Maine)\n** [[Chimenticook River]], Maine\n*** [[Eastern Lake (Kamouraska)|Eastern Lake]], Quebec and Maine\n**** [[Pointes River]], Quebec\n** [[Pocwock River]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[West Branch Pocwock Stream]], Quebec and Maine\n*** [[East Branch Pocwock Stream]], Maine\n* [[Little Black River (Saint John River tributary)|Little Black River]] (named \"Little Black River\" in Maine), Quebec and Maine\n** [[West Branch Little Black River (Quebec\u2013Maine)|West Branch Little Black River tributary)]]\n** [[Campbell Branch Little Black River]], Quebec and Maine\n* [[St. Francis River (Maine)|St. Francis River]] ({{lang-fr|rivi\u00e8re Saint-Fran\u00e7ois}}), Quebec and Maine\n** [[Lake Pohenegamook]], Quebec\n*** [[Boucan\u00e9e River]], Quebec\n** [[Blue River (Saint Francis River tributary)|Blue River]], Quebec\n*** [[Little Blue River (Quebec)|Little Blue River]], Quebec\n**** [[Southwest Blue River (Little Blue River tributary)|Southwest Blue River]], Quebec\n**** [[Prairies River (Little Blue River tributary)|Prairies River]], Quebec\n* [[Crocs River]], Quebec and [[New Brunswick]]\n* [[Baker River (New Brunswick)|Baker River]]\n** [[Branche \u00e0 Jerry]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n** [[North Baker River (Qu\u00e9bec-New Brunswick)|North Baker River]]\n* [[Madawaska River (Saint John River tributary)|Madawaska River]], Quebec and New Brunswick (see next section)\n* [[Iroquois River (Saint John River tributary)|Iroquois River]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n}}\n\n===Saint John River \u2013 watershed of Madawaska River \u2013 Quebec and New Brunswick===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Madawaska River (Saint John River tributary)|Madawaska River]], Quebec and [[New Brunswick]]\n** [[Truite River (Madawaska River tributary)|Truite River]], Quebec and New Brunswick\n*** [[Little Truite River (Truite River), Madawaska County]], New Brunswick\n** [[Perches River (Madawaska River)]], Quebec\n*** [[Sapins River (Perches River tributary)|Sapins River]], Quebec\n** [[Creuse River (Temiscouata Lake)|Creuse River]], Quebec\n** [[Cabano River (Temiscouata Lake)|Cabano River]], Quebec\n** [[Little Savane River (Temiscouata Lake)|Little Savane River]], Quebec\n** [[Caldwell River (Temiscouata Lake)|Caldwell River]], Quebec\n*** [[Lachaine River]], Quebec\n*** [[Savane River (Caldwell River tributary)|Savane River]], Quebec\n** [[Ashberish River]], Quebec\n** [[Touladi River]], Quebec\n*** [[Aigles River (Touladi River tributary)|Aigles River]], Quebec\n**** [[Sisime des Aigles River]], Quebec\n*** [[Orient River (Touladi River tributary)|Orient River]], Quebec\n**** [[Verte River (Orient River tributary)|Verte River]], Quebec\n*** [[Squatec River]], Quebec\n**** [[Owen River (Qu\u00e9bec)|Owen River]], Quebec\n** [[Bouleaux River (Madawaska River tributary)|Bouleaux River]], Quebec\n}}\n\n== Connecticut River \u2013 Quebec and New Hampshire ==\n\n* [[Connecticut River]], [[New Hampshire]]\n** [[Halls Stream]], Quebec and [[New Hampshire]]\n\n{{Expand list|date=August 2016}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of rivers of Canada]]\n* [[List of longest rivers of Canada]]\n* [[List of Hudson Bay rivers]]\n* [[List of tributaries of St. Lawrence River]]\n* [[List of tributaries of Gulf of St. Lawrence River]]\n* [[List of rivers of New Brunswick]]\n* [[List of rivers of Ontario]]\n* [[List of rivers of Newfoundland and Labrador]]\n* [[List of rivers of Montreal Island]]\n* [[List of rivers of Maine]]\n* [[List of rivers of New Hampshire]]\n* [[List of rivers of Vermont]]\n* [[List of rivers of New York State]]\n* [[List of rivers of the Americas]]\n* [[List of canals of Quebec]]\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.quebecgeographique.gouv.qc.ca/ Geography of Quebec \u2013 Gouvernment of Quebec]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Quebec topics}}\n{{Canada topic|List of rivers of}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of rivers of Canada|Qu